column5: Anyone been on Sabaskong around Morson or Nestor Falls? Heading up tomorrow morning for the week. Targeting walleye and musky. Might even chase some big crappies. What's been happening?

I was up last week and fishing was pretty good. Picked up some walleyes for dinner and trolled for muskie's. Got a couple, nothing big but some huge pike. Didn't have time to try for any crappies. Looks like you are going to have some nice weather.
